author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3370 Extend multiple file handling to IMultipartWebRequest
Add support for multiple file uploads with a single post request (HTML5 <input type="file" multiple />).

Added an additional method to FileUploadField - #getFileUploads() which returns all uploaded files. The old #getFileUpload() is still there and it returns getFileUploads().get(0) for backward compatibility.
